  <h1>Responsive Grid</h1>
  <p class="lead">Grid layout patterns using <code>layout-grid</code> and CSS Grid. Responsive by default with no media queries required.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Vanilla Breeze provides automatic responsive grids through the <code>layout-grid</code> custom element. This snippet includes additional patterns for specific use cases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Auto-fit grids</strong> - Columns wrap automatically based on available space</li>
        <li><strong>Fixed column grids</strong> - Exact column counts with responsive fallbacks</li>
        <li><strong>Asymmetric layouts</strong> - Sidebar + content patterns</li>
        <li><strong>Masonry-like layouts</strong> - Dense packing for varied-height items</li>
        <li><strong>Named area grids</strong> - Dashboard-style complex layouts</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

